ygData.messageBody:
Hey all fellow enchanters,
I joind a very powerfull group and went into PAW last night,,,, there for a long time, had a great spawn killing pattern,
always killing Named shamans, and commanders. GREAT Exp!
anyway, i found a few interesting things, and i was wondering if anyone knew anything about them? perhaps they are quest items? or something else.

1) Skull of (damn, i forget his name, i'll post it when i get it...sorry) but i got a skull, and it wont sell, i was not going to sell it, thats just how i test it to see if its anything more.

2) Words of Tyranny:: its a parchement? i think its part of a researchable spell, but i cannot read it, since i cannot research yet.


3) thisis not a found item, but something a Mage told me that was in our party. he said he heard rumors of being able to mount a certain skull on the Totem staff??? can anyone confirm this??



Thanx!!!

Aeramus (Bristlebane)
